ng_Bin\" title=\"Mini-Shipping Bin\">Mini-Shipping Bin</a> • <a href=\"/Sewing_Machine\" title=\"Sewing Machine\">Sewing Machine</a> • <a href=\"/Staircase\" title=\"Staircase\">Staircase</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_Blessings\" title=\"Statue Of Blessings\">Statue Of Blessings</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_The_Dwarf_King\" title=\"Statue Of The Dwarf King\">Statue Of The Dwarf King</a> •  <a href=\"/Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\">Telephone</a> • <a href=\"/Tent_Kit\" title=\"Tent Kit\">Tent Kit</a> • <a href=\"/Tools\" title=\"Tools\">Tools</a> • <a href=\"/Workbench\" title=\"Workbench\">Workbench</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413191107\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.171 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.194 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 8912/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 22481/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2162/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3760/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.003/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 519 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  100.212      1 -total\n 40.97%   41.058      6 Template:Description\n 38.39%   38.467      1 Template:Infobox\n 16.29%   16.321     10 Template:Name\n 12.42%   12.445      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n  3.35%    3.358      2 Template:History\n  2.65%    2.655      4 Template:Price\n  1.91%    1.912      2 Template:Version\n  1.79%    1.794      1 Template:NavboxEquipment\n  1.30%    1.305      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2157-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413191107 and revision id 190647\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Sprinkler\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|ingredients = {{Name|Copper Bar|1}}{{Name|Iron Bar|1}}\n|sellprice   = 100\n|quality     = false\n|recipe      = [[File:Farming Skill Icon.png|24px]] [[Farming]] Level 2\n}}\n{{For|all types of sprinklers|Crafting#Sprinklers|R=This article is about the specific item.}}\nThe '''Sprinkler''' is a [[Crafting|crafted]] item that waters 4 tiles (above, below, and to the right and left of it) every morning. Only tilled tiles will be watered. The Sprinkler is unlocked at [[Farming]] level 2.\n\n[[Crafting#Sprinklers|Sprinklers]] can water [[Slime Hutch]] troughs, but cannot be used to water [[Garden Pot]]s or the [[Animals#Cat or Dog|pet's]] water bowl. Sprinklers cannot be placed on sand.\n\nA [[Torch]] can be placed on a Sprinkler to provide minimal lighting in the dark.\n\n[[File:Sprinklerexample.png|140px]]\n\n==Types==\n{{#lst:Crafting|craftingsprinklers}}\n\n==Upgrades==\n<section begin=\"upgrades\" />\nUpgrades can be attached onto a placed sprinkler. Picking up the sprinkler will remove the upgrade without destroying it.\n\nOnly one upgrade can be used at a time on a single sprinkler.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Sprinklers\n!Purchase Price\n|-\n|[[File:Pressure Nozzle.png|center]]\n|[[Pressure Nozzle]] (4)\n|{{Description|Pressure Nozzle}}\n|[[File:PressureNozzleSprinklers.png|center]]\n|{{Price|20|Gem}}\n|-\n|[[File:Enricher.png|center]]\n|[[Enricher]] (4)\n|{{Description|Enricher}}\n|[[File:EnricherSprinklers.png|center]]\n|{{Price|20|Gem}}\n|}<section end=\"upgrades\" />\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|dislike=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Sebastian,Linus,Leo,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jas,Vincent,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nThe Sprinkler is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Quests==\nThe Sprinkler is not used in any [[quests]].\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.5|Improved sprinklers: Sprinklers can now water [[Slime Hutch|slime hutch]] troughs. [[Hoes]] no longer remove sprinklers. Added [[enricher]] and [[Pressure Nozzle|pressure nozzle]] upgrades.}}\n{{History|1.6|Can now have a [[Torch]] placed on it.}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n\n[[de:Sprinkler]]\n[[es:Aspersor]]\n[[fr:Arroseur]]\n[[it:Irrigatore]]\n[[ja:スプリンクラー]]\n[[ko:스프링클러]]\n[[hu:Öntöző]]\n[[pt:Aspersor]]\n[[ru:Спринклер]]\n[[tr:Fıskiye]]\n[[zh:洒水器]]"
